Our Founding Fathers who, wishing for Life, Liberty, and Happiness, fought a bloody war against history and tyranny and set up the most free system of self governance that ever was. 5. The Patriots who “watered” the tree of liberty with blood, sweat and tears. 6. Our children and wives who continue to give us someone to love and share our life’s mission. 7. Donald J Trump, for being the greatest leader of the greatest movement “by the people and for the the people” 8. J.D. Vance 9. RFK 10. Scott Pressler 11. r/theDonald and Patriots.win for being the best dang group of humans, with whom we’ve had the pleasure of Shitposting.
